# Source Discovery Verification

{% include "runtime/partial/step_verification_contract.md.j2" %}

Derive sibling `state.json` from the current input path. Read the current input and result, the runtime-owned `SourceDiscoveryState`, all four JSONL files referenced by that state, and every evidence artifact needed for the decisions. Treat an absent referenced JSONL as empty when no record of that type has been completed. Do not write or rewrite any artifact, invoke the append command, or repair state during verification.

